---
import Terminal from "./ui/Terminal.astro";
import Badge from "./ui/Badge.astro";
---

<section class="py-24 bg-bg-base">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal">
      <p class="section-label">Agent-native</p>
      <h2 class="mb-4">Built for agents. Not retrofitted.</h2>
      <p class="body-lg max-w-[640px] mx-auto mb-4 text-text-secondary">
        Your AI agents generate tasks, track progress, and need structured
        output to reason about what to do next. oru treats them as first-class
        participants — not afterthoughts bolted onto a human-only interface.
      </p>
      <p class="body max-w-[640px] mx-auto text-text-tertiary">
        Every command returns JSON. Creates are idempotent. Metadata is
        arbitrary. There is no interaction model to work around.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-16 max-md:grid-cols-1 reveal"
      data-delay="80"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 min-w-0">
        <div class="text-center">
          <Badge>Human-friendly</Badge>
        </div>
        <Terminal title="orulist">
          <span class="line"
            ><span class="prompt">$ </span><span class="cmd">oru</span>
            <span class="sub">list</span></span
          >
          <span class="line"
            ><span class="output"> # Title Priority Due Status</span></span
          >
          <span class="line"
            ><span class="output"> 1 Refactor auth middleware </span><span
              class="val">high</span
            ><span class="output"> Fri Feb 20 todo</span></span
          >
          <span class="line"
            ><span class="output"> 2 Write migration tests </span><span
              class="val">medium</span
            ><span class="output"> — in-progress</span></span
          >
          <span class="line"
            ><span class="output"> 3 Update API docs </span><span class="val"
              >low</span
            ><span class="output"> — todo</span></span
          >
        </Terminal>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 min-w-0">
        <div class="text-center">
          <Badge>Agent-friendly</Badge>
        </div>
        <Terminal title="orulist --json">
          <span class="line"
            ><span class="prompt">$ </span><span class="cmd">oru</span>
            <span class="sub">list</span>
            <span class="flag">--json</span></span
          >
          <span class="line"><span class="output">[</span></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output"> {"{"}</span></span>
          <span class="line"
            ><span class="output"> </span><span class="key">"id"</span><span
              class="output"
              >:
            </span><span class="str">"019414a2-7b1a-..."</span><span
              class="output">,</span
            ></span
          >
          <span class="line"
            ><span class="output"> </span><span class="key">"title"</span><span
              class="output"
              >:
            </span><span class="str">"Refactor auth middleware"</span><span
              class="output">,</span
            ></span
          >
          <span class="line"
            ><span class="output"> </span><span class="key">"status"</span
            ><span class="output"
              >:
            </span><span class="str">"todo"</span><span class="output">,</span
            ></span
          >
          <span class="line"
            ><span class="output"> </span><span class="key">"priority"</span
            ><span class="output">: </span><span class="str">"high"</span
            ></span
          >
          <span class="line"><span class="output"> {"}"}</span></span>
          <span class="line"><span class="output">]</span></span>
        </Terminal>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-md:grid-cols-1">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 min-w-0 reveal" data-delay="80">
        <h3 class="text-[22px]">Idempotent creates. Safe retries.</h3>
        <p class="body text-text-secondary">
          Agents retry. Network calls fail. oru's <code
            class="font-mono text-[13px] bg-bg-surface px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-accent"
            >--id</code
          > flag lets agents supply their own UUIDv7, making creates idempotent. Run
          it twice, get one task.
        </p>
        <Terminal title="idempotent creates">
          <span class="line"
            ><span class="prompt">$ </span><span class="cmd">oru</span>
            <span class="sub">add</span>
            <span class="str">"Deploy to staging"</span>
            <span class="flag">--id</span>
            <span class="val">019414a3-8c2b-7e5f-9d4a-2b3c4d5e6f70</span></span
          >
          <span class="line"
            ><span class="output">Created task 019414a3</span></span
          >
          <span class="blank"></span>
          <span class="line"
            ><span class="prompt">$ </span><span class="cmd">oru</span>
            <span class="sub">add</span>
            <span class="str">"Deploy to staging"</span>
            <span class="flag">--id</span>
            <span class="val">019414a3-8c2b-7e5f-9d4a-2b3c4d5e6f70</span></span
          >
          <span class="line"
            ><span class="output">Task already exists. No-op.</span></span
          >
        </Terminal>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 min-w-0 reveal" data-delay="160">
        <h3 class="text-[22px]">Arbitrary metadata.</h3>
        <p class="body text-text-secondary">
          Agents need to stash context — which PR spawned a task, which model
          created it, which run it belongs to. The <code
            class="font-mono text-[13px] bg-bg-surface px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-accent"
            >--meta</code
          > flag takes arbitrary key-value pairs.
        </p>
        <Terminal title="metadata">
          <span class="line"
            ><span class="prompt">$ </span><span class="cmd">oru</span>
            <span class="sub">add</span>
            <span class="str">"Review PR feedback"</span> \</span
          >
          <span class="line">
            <span class="flag">--meta</span>
            <span class="val">agent=claude-code</span> \</span
          >
          <span class="line">
            <span class="flag">--meta</span>
            <span class="val">pr=142</span> \</span
          >
          <span class="line">
            <span class="flag">--meta</span>
            <span class="val">run=a1b2c3</span></span
          >
          <span class="line"
            ><span class="output">Created task 019414a4</span></span
          >
        </Terminal>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
